document.full_text: goaltender henrik lundqvist kept the rangers in a dull game against last-place ottawa, but they lost, 2-1, on a shootout goal by erik karlsson in the fifth round.
document.title: n.h.l. roundup | senators 2, rangers 1 - shootout: lundqvist is sharp, but rangers are not
